snippet.textDisplay: Its not attack who gives you goals... Its Midfield who create them.... MSN had Busi, Inesta and Xavi (for some period). You can't create anything if you don't have a consistency in Midfield. If anyone watch Barcelona week in week out...they know that barca have so much rotation in midfield... Iniesta, Xavi and Busi have played almost a decade together and its almost super tough to fill in their shoes. Its Midfield who keeps the possession, they create , they recover, they pass through. We all are used to Barca dominating the game with ball control. Its not that easy. Barca DNA is hard to find both in players and coaches... Let see how season go from here.
